		<td><b>pitch-related tools for PPMCK users</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Freq2Reg: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://cakdude.webs.com/freq2reg%20v0_112.zip">http://cakdude.webs.com/freq2reg%20v0_112.zip</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />Batch-converts a list of true frequencies (expressed in hz) to @n values. Contains option to create a txt file readable by Phrase Express, so you can map the @n values to keys on your PC keyboard in a few simple steps. Highly useful for people who like to experiment with microtonal scales.
<br />
<br />Porta2EP: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://cakdude.webs.com/porta2ep%20v0_1.zip">http://cakdude.webs.com/porta2ep%20v0_1.zip</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />Creates EP commands from starting @n, ending @n, and number of frames. Useful for implementing accurate portamento in your MML.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


